Dialogue: 2,0:00:01.50,0:00:02.92,Transcription,,0,0,0,,Hello and welcome!
Dialogue: 2,0:00:03.66,0:00:07.20,Transcription,,0,0,0,,In this small presentation I would like to introduce you to Whispersub
Dialogue: 2,0:00:07.20,0:00:07.82,Transcription,,0,0,0,,to you.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:08.56,0:00:13.88,Transcription,,0,0,0,,With this tool you can extract audio tracks from MKV files,
Dialogue: 2,0:00:14.48,0:00:16.18,Transcription,,0,0,0,,automatically transcribe them
Dialogue: 2,0:00:16.77,0:00:19.52,Transcription,,0,0,0,,and merge them with existing subtitles.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:20.40,0:00:22.64,Transcription,,0,0,0,,Particularly practical is that different
Dialogue: 2,0:00:22.64,0:00:24.96,Transcription,,0,0,0,,languages are supported and
Dialogue: 2,0:00:24.96,0:00:27.68,Transcription,,0,0,0,,romanization into Latin script is possible.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:28.46,0:00:28.68,Transcription,,0,0,0,,Even
Dialogue: 2,0:00:28.68,0:00:31.88,Transcription,,0,0,0,,background noise is not a major problem.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:32.35,0:00:34.38,Transcription,,0,0,0,,Because Whispersub can separate voices
Dialogue: 2,0:00:34.38,0:00:36.38,Transcription,,0,0,0,,from the rest of the audio track.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:37.10,0:00:39.98,Transcription,,0,0,0,,This makes the creation of precise and clear
Dialogue: 2,0:00:40.04,0:00:42.10,Transcription,,0,0,0,,subtitles much easier.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:43.10,0:00:44.98,Transcription,,0,0,0,,Feel free to try it out yourself!

